Canonical
=========

http://www.seomoz.org/blog/canonical-url-tag-the-most-important-advancement-in-seo-practices-since-sitemaps

Example
=======

<%= canonical %>
<link href="http://localhost:3000/main" rel="canonical" />


<%= canonical(:action => 'test') %>
<link href="http://localhost:3000/main/test" rel="canonical" />


